Add @prisma/extension-accelerate and update build scripts
Added @prisma/extension-accelerate to dependencies. Updated build and postinstall scripts to run 'prisma generate' before building, ensuring Prisma client is generated automatically.

Refactor UI components to use radix-ui package
Replaces individual @radix-ui/react-* imports with unified imports from the radix-ui package across all UI components. Updates package.json to use radix-ui instead of separate Radix UI dependencies, simplifying dependency management and imports.

Add glossary management and integration
Introduces glossary support with new Prisma models, tRPC router, and UI components for managing glossaries and terms. Integrates glossary selection into book drafts and applies glossary terms during translation for consistent terminology. Updates DeepSeek client, translation service, and validators to support glossary usage. Refactors dashboard layout and sidebar to include glossaries tab.
